As promised earlier:

ar_hide_and_seek_house_lite is a port of stripped-down vershion the hide_and_seek_house20 map from the CSGO game.

Description of the map from the author:

This is a map for hide and seek. There are lots of cool hideouts and passages on the map. I tried to make every element on the map perfectly finished the way I wanted. There is one interesting place worth seeing Have fun.



//  - Well, now the FPS is in perfect order.
